《路易吉洋樓》是2001年11月最暢銷的遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/luigismansion/news.html?sid=2833937|title=November software sales charts|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|last=Gerstmann|first=Jeff|date=2001-12-19|accessdate=2007-11-17|archive-date=2014-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325002329/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/november-software-sales-charts/1100-2833937/|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管此遊戲在日本只售出了約348,000套遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.japan-gamecharts.com/gc.php|title=Japan GameCube charts|accessdate=2007-11-09|publisher=Japan Game Charts|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070723025415/http://www.japan-gamecharts.com/gc.php|archive-date=2007-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但此遊戲仍然成為了第五暢銷的任天堂GameCube遊戲<ref name="USsales">{{cite web|url=http://www.the-magicbox.com/Chart-USPlatinum.shtml|title=US Platinum Videogame Chart|publisher=The Magic Box|accessdate=2008-12-05|archive-date=2007-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106203333/http://www.the-magicbox.com/Chart-USPlatinum.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且至今已售出逾250萬套遊戲。<ref name="USsales"/>此遊戲亦是首個獲任天堂頒發玩家選擇獎的任天堂GameCube遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cube.ign.com/articles/383/383504p1.html|title=Nintendo Expands Player's Choice Line-up|publisher=IGN|date=2003-01-23|accessdate=2007-11-17|archive-date=2008-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080605164438/http://cube.ign.com/articles/383/383504p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《路易吉洋樓》主要獲得正面的評價。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]給予此遊戲7.9/10分，並指出此遊戲「擁有一些新穎的元素」。<ref name="GameSpot">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/luigismansion/review.html|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|last=Satterfield|first=Shane|date=2001-11-07|accessdate=2007-06-29|archive-date=2011-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110907041552/http://www.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/luigismansion/review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>遊戲雜誌《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》給予此遊戲4/5分，並指出此遊戲「很過癮，且重玩性很高。」<ref name="NP">{{cite journal|date=November 2001|journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]]|publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]]|page=142}}</ref>。[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]則指出此遊戲擁有「良好的視覺效果、豐富的想像力和一些經典的任天堂元素。」<ref name="GameSpy">{{cite web|url=http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/november01/luigismansion/|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]|last=Williams|first=Bryn|accessdate=2007-06-29|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070626204915/http://archive.gamespy.com/reviews/november01/luigismansion/|archivedate=2007-06-26}}</ref>。

《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》指出此遊戲是「一個熟練的遊戲設計例子」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/nintendo/gamecube/games/reviews/18323.shtml|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[GamePro|GamePro]]|author=Tokyodrifter|date=2001-11-19|accessdate=2008-02-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607133310/http://www.gamepro.com/nintendo/gamecube/games/reviews/18323.shtml|archivedate=2011-06-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]指出「此遊戲的畫面相當漂亮，且遊戲內容非常有趣。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/oldsite/games/gamecube/adventure/luigis_mansion.htm|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]|last=Liu|first=Johnny|accessdate=2008-02-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514042107/http://www.gamerevolution.com/oldsite/games/gamecube/adventure/luigis_mansion.htm|archivedate=2008-05-14}}</ref>。而 雜誌《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》則給予此遊戲9/10分，並將它稱為「宮本茂最好的作品」。<ref name="GI">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200111/R03.0806.1027.02128.htm?CS_pid=220001|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|last=Reiner|first=Andrew|accessdate=2007-06-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071004212916/http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200111/R03.0806.1027.02128.htm?CS_pid=220001|archivedate=2007-10-04|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

另一方面，[[IGN|IGN]]將遊戲的配音描述為「可愛、幽默和令人滿意的」，並給予此遊戲7/10分。<ref name="IGN">{{cite web|url=http://cube.ign.com/articles/165/165453p1.html|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=IGN|last=Casamassina|first=Matt|date=2001-11-16|accessdate=2007-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070606150559/http://cube.ign.com/articles/165/165453p1.html|archive-date=2007-06-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>GameSpy指出此遊戲的背景音樂「微妙、有趣、完全適合整個遊戲。」<ref name="GameSpy"/>，而雜誌《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》則給予此遊戲34/40分，授予金獎，並稱讚其操作系統。<ref name="Famitsu">{{cite web|url=http://cube.ign.com/articles/098/098227p1.html|title=Famitsu Gives GameCube Gold|publisher=IGN|date=2001-09-12|accessdate=2008-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070508225128/http://cube.ign.com/articles/098/098227p1.html|archive-date=2007-05-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

此作主要被批評遊戲長度過短。GameSpot指出「此遊戲過短的遊戲長度抹煞了其優點」。<ref name="GameSpot"/>GameSpy亦批評遊戲長度，指出此遊戲能於6小時內完成。<ref name="GameSpy"/>[[Allgame|Allgame]]指出此遊戲「未能提供一個有凝聚力的遊戲體驗，全因遊戲長度過短。」<ref name="allgame">{{cite web|url=http://www.allgame.com/cg/agg.dll?p=agg&sql=1:34975~T1|title=Luigi's Mansion review|publisher=[[Allgame|Allgame]]|last=Thompson|first=Jon|accessdate=2008-02-06}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。IGN認為遊戲玩法欠佳，並指出遊戲玩法是「可預測的，公式化的。」<ref name="IGN"/>。電視節目《[[X-Play|X-Play]]》亦批評此遊戲的遊戲玩法，並指出此遊戲「令瑪利歐系列支持者失望」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/videos/18977/XPlay_Bad_Mario_Games.html|title=X-Play: Bad Mario Games|publisher=[[G4_(TV_channel)|G4]]|accessdate=2008-06-08|archive-date=2008-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423210212/http://www.g4tv.com/xplay/videos/18977/XPlay_Bad_Mario_Games.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管如此，《[[官方任天堂雜誌|官方任天堂雜誌]]》仍將此遊戲列為「史上100強任天堂遊戲」的第99位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/article.php?id=7188|title=100-81 ONM|publisher=[[Official_Nintendo_Magazine|ONM]]|accessdate=2009-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090223134327/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/article.php?id=7188|archive-date=2009-02-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2002年，遊戲獲[[英國電影電視藝術學院|英國電影電視藝術學院]]頒發互動娛樂獎。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/luigismansion/news.html?sid=2885427&mode=all|title=BAFTA 2002 awards announced|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|last=Parker |first=Sam|date=2002-10-11|accessdate=2008-02-06}}</ref>

